reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Attractive and functional.
reviews.reviewText: Was looking for a gooseneck and though this lamp doesn't perform quite like one, the other features make up for it. Including wireless phone charger, display with date, temp and time along with three different light modes. Also looks sleek and nice on my desk. Glad I purchased instead of the gooseneck.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Lamp for Price
reviews.reviewText: Ordered this lamp to put on my desk since I work from home. Love the fact that it has 3 different light settings, so depending on the time of the day I can have different lighting which helps with the tiredness in my eyes. Also absolute love you can charge your phone on it. The instructions it comes with were pretty good, but there were definitely some information left out, but I was able to come back to Amazon and search the question and got it answered super quickly. Once you get the hang of setting the display it’s super easy. Really impresssd with this light overall for the price it was. Also gives off a good amount of light but is not huge so doesn’t take up to much room on my desk!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Awesome features works well. Looks nice
reviews.reviewText: I like the numerous features. All work as stated in the description EXCLUDING the qi.charger. that doesn't charge my Samsung android that does have the qi charging ability. But there's a USB so that's fine. The light has 5 different brightness modes. 3 different light temp.modes (like warm, cold or natural light). You have to set the clock from the back of the clock screen.Play with it and you'll figure it out. To turn the clock backlight OFF press and hold the power button on the lamp. Gotta change the year and make the eight date, time etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This little lamp is great. Packed with features you’d expect in a much more expensive lamp. Several different light modes from reading to very dim. The clock and temperature come in handy. Bonus is the usb outlet for charging other items plus the fast charger for iPhones. You won’t regret buying this table lamp. I will be purchasing another one for my desk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great Lamp.I love the touch system to set lighting mode & the wireless charger

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Way better than I thought it would be . Great light.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bought 3 of these!
reviews.reviewText: We bought one at a certain discount store whom shall remain nameless....ahem...costmore. Paid over 30.00 for 1 lamp. It fell once and the plug in broke, thinking you could use a USB to run it, bought a USB plug, NOPE! Found these on Amazon, bought 1, loved it, bought another, loved it so we bought another. They are great lights! You can adjust the brightness, the "color" they have wireless charging for your phone and usb ports if you want. They are so slim they can go pretty much anywhere without a huge bulky lamp in the way of things. We have one on an end table and it's great! Love these. I'm looking for more places to put these things to get more! They are cheap in price but they are NOT cheap, lol.
